-This release is based on an older project called mini-fake-dns-server http://www.tranquilidadtecnologica.com/2006/04/servidor-fake-dns-en-python.html 

Description: 
 "You can redirect DNS requests to specific Domain Name with automated Resolving eg: * -> mydomain.dyndns-server.com
   This script will redirect all domain names to mydomain.dyndns-server.com"

Changes:
 -Added DNS resolving from ip to Domain Name for Dynamic IP support
 -Added threading and improved performance

Instructions:
0. Edit Domain_Name and sleeptime variables to your needs
1. Run server: python dns.py
3. Exit: ctrl+c



